#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "10 Apr, 2026"
msgstr "10 Apr, 2026"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Release"
msgstr "版本"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "New features"
msgstr "新特性"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Annotations browser: Allow grouping results by any field"
msgstr "标注浏览器：允许按任意字段对结果进行分组"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Handle native pinch to zoom gesture on touchpads the same as "
"the pinch to zoom on touchscreens. Default action is to change font size."
msgstr "电子书阅读器：统一触摸板与触摸屏的原生捏合缩放手势。默认动作为调整字体大小。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: Implement full offline mode when using HTTPS connections to "
"the content server"
msgstr "内容服务器：支持在 HTTPS 连接下开启全功能离线使用模式"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Bug fixes"
msgstr "Bug修复"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Fix a regression in the previous release that caused "
"annotations/last read information to not be saved in e-book files"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：修复了上一版无法将标注/进度保存到电子书文件的回归错误。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Closes tickets"
msgstr "解决的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "AI: Make the GitHub backend a bit more robust"
msgstr "AI：提高 GitHub 后端稳定性"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"AI: OpenRouter backend: Fix reasoning level \"auto\" disabling all reasoning"
msgstr "AI：OpenRouter 后端：修复推理级别设为“自动”时会导致所有推理功能被禁用的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: Read book: Fix regression causing error during searching"
msgstr "内容服务器：阅读书籍：修复导致搜索时报错的回归错误"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Content server: Fix opening results from full text search not working"
msgstr "内容服务器：修复无法从全文搜索结果中打开书籍的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a couple of minor regress in the new Full text search view introduced in"
" the previous release"
msgstr "修复上一版本中新引入的全文搜索视图里的几处细微回归错误"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"MTP driver: Linux: Fix a rare crash when connecting devices with large "
"collections"
msgstr "MTP 驱动：Linux：修复连接存有大量书籍的设备时发生的罕见崩溃"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix cover not being set when adding files to existing book records with no "
"cover"
msgstr "修复在为没有封面的现有书籍记录添加文件时，封面未被正确设置的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "New news sources"
msgstr "新的新闻源"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "{0} by {1}"
msgstr "{0} 自 {1}"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Improved news sources"
msgstr "改进的新闻源"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "27 Mar, 2026"
msgstr "27 Mar, 2026"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Full text search: A new cards based view of full text search results with "
"book covers"
msgstr "全文搜索：搜索结果支持“卡片模式”，可直接查看书籍封面"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"To perform a full text search, click the \"FT\" button on the left of the "
"search bar. The old compact result view can be re-activated by clicking the "
"button to the left of the search bar in the Full text search window."
msgstr "若要进行全文搜索，请点击搜索栏左侧的 “FT” 按钮。在全文搜索窗口中，点击搜索栏左侧的按钮，即可重新启用旧版紧凑结果视图。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"A new \"word-prefix\" completion mode that shows matches that have any word "
"starting with the typed in letters"
msgstr "新增“单词前缀 (word-prefix)”补全模式：可显示任何以输入字母开头的单词匹配项"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Bookshelves: Add option to have the height of books be constant per group"
msgstr "书架：新增选项，支持将每组书籍的高度设置为固定统一"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Edit book: File list: Allow using Ctrl+Shift+Left/Right to move an item to "
"top/bottom of the list"
msgstr "编辑书籍：文件列表：支持使用 Ctrl+Shift+左/右方向键将项目移至列表最顶端或最末尾"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Fix notes being lost when changing the lookup name of custom column"
msgstr "修复了更改自定义列的“查找名称”时导致笔记丢失的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Fix using the slower/faster buttons causing a chapter skip "
"when using the Piper neural speech backend"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：修复了在使用 Piper 神经网络语音后端时，点击加速/减速按钮会导致跳过章节的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server viewer: Fix annotations being not synced to the server in "
"some Android devices when using the Firefox browser"
msgstr "内容服务器阅读器：修复了在部分安卓设备上使用火狐 (Firefox) 浏览器时，批注无法同步至服务器的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Force kill calibre.exe on quit to workaround hang in interpreter "
"shutdown on some systems"
msgstr "Windows：修复部分系统退出时卡死的问题，改为在关闭程序时强制杀掉进程"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"TXT Output: Fix asciiize option not applying to generated inline Table of "
"Contents"
msgstr "TXT 输出：修复了“转换非 ASCII 字符”选项对生成的内嵌目录无效的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Disallow background images from the internet. This was an "
"unused feature anyway (CVE-2026-33205)"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：禁用从互联网加载背景图片的功能。这本就是一个弃用的功能 (CVE-2026-33205)"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"TXT Input: Ensure resource files are read only from book contents "
"(CVE-2026-33206)"
msgstr "TXT 输入：确保资源文件仅从书籍内容中读取 (CVE-2026-33206)"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Only apply changes to text fields in the book list when the new value is "
"different from the old"
msgstr "优化书籍列表编辑：仅在文本内容发生变化时执行更新操作"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Completions: Update list of completion suggestions when cursor is moved"
msgstr "补全：移动光标时更新补全建议列表"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "13 Mar, 2026"
msgstr "13 Mar, 2026"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Allow creating a column to display reading progress"
msgstr "允许创建用于显示阅读进度的列"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Reading progress comes from the calibre E-book viewer. To create the column,"
" go to Preferences->Add your own columns, click the plus button and finally "
"click on the \"Read progress\" link."
msgstr "阅读进度数据来自 calibre 电子书阅读器。要创建该列，请前往“首选项 -> 添加自定义列”，点击加号按钮，最后点击“阅读进度”链接。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Annotations browser: Allow filtering by highlight style"
msgstr "标注浏览器：允许按高亮样式筛选"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Add an option to display the pages from the paper book page "
"list (when available) while also showing the last page number"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：添加显示纸质书页码列表（如有）的选项，同时显示最后一页页码"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Edit book: Add a tool to remove unused images, similar to the tool to remove"
" unused CSS"
msgstr "编辑书籍：添加一个删除未使用图片的工具，类似于删除未使用 CSS 的工具"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Tolino driver: support new firmware version"
msgstr "Tolino 驱动：支持新版固件"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "E-book viewer: Add a reset button to the reading stats panel"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：在阅读统计面板中添加重置按钮"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix overridden icons from config directory not switching between dark/light "
"variants on theme change"
msgstr "修复在切换主题时，配置目录下的自定义图标无法正确切换深色/浅色版本的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix: Use MOBI fallback for KFX format when downloading news periodicals"
msgstr "修复：下载新闻期刊时，若 KFX 格式不可用则回退使用 MOBI 格式"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Edit book: Restore focus to editor after showing search count popup message"
msgstr "电子书编辑器：修复显示搜索结果计数弹窗后，光标焦点未能自动回到编辑区域的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Fix a bug in KEPUB markup removal when there are empty kobo spans"
msgstr "修复 KEPUB 标记清理过程中的一个错误：该错误会在处理空的 kobo span 标签时出现"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"RB Input: Ensure files are extracted within container dir (CVE-2026-30853)"
msgstr "RB 输入：确保文件提取在容器目录内 (CVE-2026-30853)"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Book list: Fix ctrl+shift+arrow key not moving the currently selected book. "
"Fixes #2142950"
msgstr "书籍列表：修复 Ctrl+Shift+方向键无法移动当前选中书籍的问题。修复 #2142950"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "27 Feb, 2026"
msgstr "27 Feb, 2026"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "E-book viewer: Add \"reading stats\" to show reading progress"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：新增“阅读统计”功能，用于直观显示阅读进度。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Edit book: Nicer UI for changing the entries in the insert tag menu"
msgstr "编辑书籍：优化了“插入标签”菜单项的编辑界面，操作体验更佳。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Cover grid: Option to draw emblems on top of cover in Preferences->Look & "
"feel->Cover grid->Emblems"
msgstr "封面网格：在“首选项 -> 外观 -> 封面网格 -> 图标”中，新增了在封面图上方绘制图标的选项。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Cover grid: Add option to draw text flush with bottom of rendered cover"
msgstr "封面网格：新增了一个选项，可使显示的文字与渲染后的封面底部保持齐平。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"DOCX Input: Fix paragraph/list margins in documents created by LibreOffice "
"that do not have Word 2007 compatibility"
msgstr "DOCX 导入：修复了由 LibreOffice 创建且未启用 Word 2007 兼容模式的文档中，段落与列表边距显示异常的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"ODT Input: Fix a regression in the previous release that broke conversion of"
" images"
msgstr "ODT 导入：修复了上一个版本中导致图像转换失效的回归错误。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: When banning IPs for repeated login is enabled, only use the"
" IP address not any HTTP headers as the ban key (CVE-2026-27824)"
msgstr ""
"内容服务器：修复了 CVE-2026-27824 安全漏洞。在启用“多次登录失败禁用 IP”功能时，系统现在仅强制使用真实 IP "
"地址作为封禁标识，不再信任任何 HTTP 请求头。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: Sanitize content disposition received as query parameter "
"(CVE-2026-27810)"
msgstr ""
"内容服务器：修复了 CVE-2026-27810 安全漏洞。现在会对通过查询参数接收到的 content-disposition "
"进行清理，防止恶意注入。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "20 Feb, 2026"
msgstr "20 Feb, 2026"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows installer: Detect running calibre processes and ask user to shutdown"
" calibre before proceeding with installation to avoid reboots post "
"installation"
msgstr "Windows 安装程序：检测正在运行的 Calibre 进程，并要求用户在继续安装前关闭 Calibre，以避免安装完成后需要重启系统。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Improve Preferences->Tweaks getting rid of the need for double apply"
msgstr "改进“首选项 -> 优化调整”：消除在修改设置时需要执行两次“应用”操作的需求。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"KEPUB Output: When converting to KEPUB preserve cover aspect ratio "
"regardless of the setting for it in the EPUB Output to match the behavior of"
" KEPUB files from Kobo"
msgstr ""
"KEPUB 输出：在转换为 KEPUB 格式时，无论“EPUB 输出”中的相关设置如何，均保留封面宽高比，以匹配 Kobo 原生 KEPUB "
"文件的表现。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Make the new pages column value available in save to disk/send to device "
"templates"
msgstr "使新的“页数”列数值可在“保存到硬盘”或“发送到设备”的模板中使用。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Hanvon N10 device driver: Fix calibre unable to put its metadata files onto "
"the device"
msgstr "汉王 N10 设备驱动：修复了 Calibre 无法将元数据文件写入设备的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Amazon metadata download plugin: Fix incorrect series index from amazon.com"
msgstr "Amazon 元数据下载插件：修复了从 amazon.com 获取的丛书编号不正确的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression in calibre 9.0 that broke output to PDB/TCR/zTXT files"
msgstr "修复了 Calibre 9.0 中的一个退化性故障，该故障曾导致无法正常输出 PDB、TCR 和 zTXT 格式文件。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Fix calibre not exiting on quit when the wireless device driver is "
"used in calibre 9"
msgstr "Windows：修复了在 Calibre 9 中使用无线设备驱动时，程序在退出后仍无法关闭的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix error in page counting when using the calibredb command to add a book"
msgstr "修复了在使用 calibredb 命令添加书籍时出现的页数计算错误。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Completion: When sorting completion matches in contains mode ensure matches "
"are sorted first by distance from beginning and then sub-sorted "
"alphabetically"
msgstr "补全逻辑：在“包含”模式下对匹配项进行排序时，确保匹配项优先按匹配位置距离开头的距离排序，随后再按字母顺序进行次级"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Fix a regression in calibre 9 that caused tooltips to not follow "
"the color scheme"
msgstr "Windows：修复了 Calibre 9 中的一个退化性故障，该故障曾导致工具提示的颜色无法随配色方案自动切换。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"PDF Input: Fix PDF Outline not being converted to Table of Contents in "
"output document when using the calibre engine"
msgstr "PDF 输入：修复了在使用 Calibre 引擎时，无法将 PDF 大纲转换为输出文档目录的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"ODT Input: Ensure images are extracted within container (CVE-2026-26064)"
msgstr "ODT 输入：确保提取出的图像文件被限制在容器范围内（修复 CVE-2026-26064 安全漏洞）。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"PDB Input: Ensure extracted images are within the container (CVE-2026-26065)"
msgstr "PDB 输入：确保提取出的图像文件被限制在容器范围内（修复 CVE-2026-26065 安全漏洞）。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression in calibre 9.0 that caused a spurious large books merge "
"warning when merging books in the cover grid view"
msgstr "修复了 Calibre 9.0 中的一个退化性故障，该故障曾导致在“封面网格”视图下合并书籍时，会错误地弹出书籍数量过大的合并警告。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Fix harmless error popup if user tries to launch calibre multiple "
"times in quick succession"
msgstr "Windows：修复了用户在短时间内多次快速启动 Calibre 时，会弹出错误提示的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Version 9.3.1 fixes a regression in the previous release that caused a "
"spurious error message to show when merging books and a regression in "
"calibre 9.0 that broke using textures as the Cover grid background when "
"using the system theme on Windows"
msgstr ""
"版本 9.3.1 修复了上一版本中导致合并书籍时显示误报错误消息的退化故障，并修复了 Calibre 9.0 中在 Windows "
"上使用系统主题时，无法将纹理设置为封面网格背景的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "06 Feb, 2026"
msgstr "06 Feb, 2026"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"ZIP Output: Change the template engine used for HTML templating from "
"templite to Mustache, for greater safety and performance. Note that this is "
"a breaking change if you use custom templates with ZIP output "
"(CVE-2026-25731)"
msgstr ""
"ZIP 输出：将用于 HTML 模板生成的模板引擎从 templite 切换为 Mustache，以提高安全性和性能。注意：如果您在 ZIP "
"输出中使用了自定义模板，这将是一个破坏性变更（CVE-2026-25731）。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Check library: Add an option to rebuild the annotations search index"
msgstr "检查书库：新增了一个重建“标注搜索索引”的选项。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"CHM Input: Ignore internal files that have paths that end up outside the "
"container. Prevents path traversal attacks with malicious CHM files "
"(CVE-2026-25635)"
msgstr ""
"CHM 输入：忽略路径指向容器（压缩包）外部的内部文件。这可以防止利用恶意 CHM 文件进行的路径遍历攻击（CVE-2026-25635）。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"EPUB Input: Ensure font obfuscation processing happens only on files from "
"the EPUB, preventing path traversal attacks from malicious EPUB files "
"(CVE-2026-25636)"
msgstr ""
"EPUB 输入：确保字体混淆处理仅对 EPUB 内部的文件进行，以防止利用恶意 EPUB 文件进行的路径遍历攻击（CVE-2026-25636）。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Workaround for bug in Qt 6.10 causing Read Aloud in the E-book "
"viewer to crash when stopped and restarted"
msgstr "Windows：修复了 Qt 6.10 中的一个 Bug，该 Bug 曾导致电子书阅读器中的“朗读”功能在停止后重新启动时崩溃。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Fix drag and drop of books into bookshelf view not working"
msgstr "修复了拖放书籍到书架视图中无效的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Bookshelf: Fix bookshelf view blank on some macOS systems"
msgstr "书架视图：修复了书架视图在部分 macOS 系统上显示为空白的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Fix a regression in calibre 9.0 that broke the Go to page "
"function"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：修复了 Calibre 9.0 中的一个回归问题，该问题曾导致“跳转到页码”功能失效"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "E-book viewer: Fix google dictionary lookup results not legible"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：修复了谷歌字典查询结果显示不清（不可读）的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Fix PageUp/PageDown keys needing to be pressed repeatedly at "
"internal HTML file boundaries in flow mode"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：修复了在“卷轴模式”下，跨越内部HTML文件边界时需要反复按下 PageUp/PageDown 键的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Bookshelf: Avoid rendering during initial show while the view is still being"
" resized"
msgstr "书架视图：在视图调整大小的过程中，避免在初次显示时进行渲染"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression in calibre 9.0 that caused mouse wheel to scroll a full row"
" at a time in the Cover grid"
msgstr "修复了 Calibre 9.0 中的一个回归问题，该问题曾导致鼠标滚轮在封面网格视图中一次滚动整整一行"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"News download: Fix a regression in 8.11 that broke automatic cleanup of "
"downloaded HTML"
msgstr "新闻下载：修复了 8.11 版本中的一个回归问题，该问题曾导致无法自动清理下载的 HTML 文件"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Version 9.2.1 prevents the Content server from using template based searches"
" since this is insecure when the content server is used with un-"
"authenticated users"
