"Calibre 现在已原生支持编辑、查看和转换 Kobo 使用的 KEPUB 格式文件。此外，在向 Kobo 设备发送书籍时，它会自动将 EPUB "
"转换为 KEPUB（可通过右键点击 Calibre 中的 Kobo 图标进行配置）。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Connect to folder: Allow connecting a specific device"
msgstr "连接到文件夹：允许连接特定设备。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"calibre can now connect to a folder and treat it as though it is a USBMS "
"based device. This is useful particularly on Chromebooks where USB devices "
"appear as folders rather than actual devices."
msgstr ""
"Calibre 现在可以连接到一个文件夹，并将其视为基于 USBMS（USB 大容量存储）的设备。这在 Chromebook "
"上尤为实用，因为在这些设备中，USB 设备通常以文件夹而非实际物理设备的形式出现。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"When completing names for fields that contain hierarchical data in prefix "
"mode match prefixes after every period"
msgstr "在“前缀匹配模式”下补全包含层级数据的字段名称时，支持在每个分隔符（句点）后进行前缀匹配。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"ToC editor: Allow moving of multiple selected items in the Table of Contents"
msgstr "目录编辑器：允许在目录中移动多个选定的项目"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"macOS: The calibre application icons in the dock are now displayed in a "
"white frame to follow Apple's current recommended icon style"
msgstr "macOS：Calibre 应用程序图标现在显示在白色边框中，以遵循 Apple 当前推荐的图标风格"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Kobo driver: Add support for new firmware on Tolino devices"
msgstr "Kobo 驱动：新增对 Tolino 设备新固件的支持"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Book details: Add option in to suppress author search links"
msgstr "书籍详情：新增关闭作者搜索链接的选项"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression that broke tabbing to edit cells in the book list when some"
