msgstr "元数据下载：出版者/丛书转换规则：修复了包含逗号的值无法工作的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Version 8.0.1 fixes a failure to start on systems where the user had "
"previously installed the KoboTouchExtended plugin and disabled the builtin "
"KoboTouch driver"
msgstr ""
"版本 8.0.1 修复了以下问题：在用户之前安装了 KoboTouchExtended 插件并禁用了内置 KoboTouch 驱动的系统上，程序无法启动"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "14 Feb, 2025"
msgstr "14 Feb, 2025"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Allow specifying web search links that are used when clicking on item names "
"in the Book details panel for custom columns via Preferences->Add your own "
"columns"
msgstr "允许在“首选项->添加自定义列”中，为自定义列指定 Web 搜索链接；点击“书籍详情”面板中的项名称时将触发该搜索。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: When clicking on author names in the book details page "
