"DPI"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：修复了在多显示器环境下，当主显示器的 DPI 远低于副显示器时，页眉/页脚文字显示过小的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Fix series mapping rules in the metadata preferences not working"
msgstr "修复了元数据首选项中的“丛书映射规则”失效的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Fix setting custom icon for category doesn't work"
msgstr "修复了无法为类别设置自定义图标的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Kobo driver: Fix a regression that broke working with very old Kobo devices"
msgstr "Kobo 驱动：修复了一个退化性故障，该故障曾导致程序无法与极早期的 Kobo 设备正常连接。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "07 Feb, 2025"
msgstr "07 Feb, 2025"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Allow setting custom icons for items in the Tag browser by right clicking on"
" them and choosing \"Manage icon for this value\""
msgstr "允许通过右键点击标签浏览器中的项并选择“管理此项的图标”，为特定项设置自定义图标。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
