#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix viewing books via the Cover browser not working when in device view"
msgstr "设备视图：修复了在查看设备内书籍时，无法通过封面浏览器阅读书籍的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
