#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Add import and export stored template to Preferences / template functions"
msgstr "模板函数：在“首选项 -> 模板函数”中，新增了导入和导出存档模板的功能。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Various Quality-of-Life improvements to the dialog used to edit columns with"
