msgstr "Amazon 元数据插件：针对亚马逊搜索结果页面部分书籍的 HTML 结构变化进行了更新。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "29 Nov, 2024"
msgstr "29 Nov, 2024"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Read Aloud: Add an option to control the position of the "
"popup control bar. It can now be placed along the top or bottom edges so as "
"to overlap less with text."
msgstr "阅读器：朗读功能新增了控制弹出栏位置的选项。现在可以将其置于顶部或底部边缘，以减少对正文文本的遮挡。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "System tray menu: Add action to restart calibre"
msgstr "系统托盘菜单：新增了“重启 Calibre”的操作选项"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Tolino driver: Support new firmware"
msgstr "Tolino 驱动：支持新的固件版本"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Enable popup OS notifications even when system tray icon is "
"disabled to match behavior on other platforms. Notifications can be disabled"
" via Preferences->Look & feel->Disable notifications on job completion"
msgstr ""
"Windows 平台：即使禁用了系统托盘图标，现在也会显示操作系统弹出通知，以与其他平台的行为保持一致。用户仍可通过“首选项 -> 外观 -> "
"任务完成后禁用通知”来关闭此类提醒。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression that caused incorrect English transliteration of Japanese "
"text even when the UI language is set to Japanese"
msgstr "核心引擎：修复了一个回归错误。该错误曾导致即使 UI 语言已设为日语，系统仍会对日语文本进行错误的英文转写。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"macOS: Dark mode: Fix a regression that caused the scrollbar to no longer be"
" transient"
msgstr "macOS 平台：修复了深色模式下的一个回归错误。该错误曾导致滚动条无法像预期那样自动隐藏。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"DOCX Input: When some text has multiple footnotes insert a space between the"
" consecutive foot note numbers so that they are distinct"
msgstr "DOCX 导入：当文本包含多个连续脚注时，会在脚注编号之间插入空格，以确保它们清晰可辨。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"DOCX Input: Fix ToC nesting not working if the styles for the ToC levels do "
"not use integer margins"
msgstr "DOCX 导入：修复了目录嵌套失效的问题。此前，如果目录层级样式使用了非整数边距，会导致系统无法正确识别层级结构。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Fix spurious chapter transition after configuring Read aloud"
msgstr "阅读器：修复了在配置朗读功能后，页面会意外跳转到下一章节的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "PDF Input: Fix reflow of lines in files with little text not working"
msgstr "PDF 导入：修复了文字较少的文件中，行重排功能失效的问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "08 Nov, 2024"
msgstr "08 Nov, 2024"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Edit book: A new tool to create an audio overlay in EPUB files for all text "
"using the Read aloud facility"
msgstr "编辑书籍：新增工具，可使用“朗读”功能为 EPUB 文件中的所有文本创建音频"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"This allows readers of the book to listen to it with sentence tracking, even"
" if they do not have a functioning text-to-speech system in the reading "
"software. You can even assign different voices to different parts of the "
"text for a more immersive experience. The tool is available from the Tools "
"menu in the book editor."
msgstr ""
"这使得书籍读者可以在阅读软件中同时收听带有句子跟踪的音频，即使该软件本身没有正常运作的TTS系统。您甚至可以为文本的不同部分指定不同的声音，以获得更具沉浸感的体验。该工具可在书籍编辑器的“工具”菜单中找到。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Dark mode: make scrollbar more visible with higher contrast and rounded "
"corners"
msgstr "深色模式：增强了滚动条的对比度并采用圆角设计，使其更加清晰易辨"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: In flow mode when scrolling across internal file boundaries "
"using the mouse wheel/touchpad have a short half second pause to ease the "
"transition. Can be controlled via the Scrolling section of the Viewer "
"preferences."
msgstr ""
"阅读器：在卷轴模式下，当使用鼠标滚轮或触控板滚动跨越内部文件边界时，新增了半秒钟的短暂停顿，以使过渡更加平滑。用户可在阅读器首选项的“滚动”部分自行调节。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"ebook-meta.exe: Add an option to disallow rendered cover of first page for "
"EPUB"
msgstr "命令行工具：ebook-meta.exe 新增了一个选项，用于禁止将 EPUB 的第一页渲染为书籍封面。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Book details: Add an action to download the cover to the context menu when "
"right clicking the cover"
msgstr "书籍详情：在右键点击封面时，右键菜单中新增了“下载封面”的操作选项。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Read aloud: Add a restore defaults button to the configuration dialog"
msgstr "朗读功能：在配置对话框中新增了“恢复默认值”按钮。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Auto adding: Allow excluding arbitrary file types not just known book file "
"types"
msgstr "自动添加：支持排除任意文件类型，而不再局限于已知的书籍文件格式。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Edit metadata dialog: Add an action to open the book's folder to the context"
" menu of the formats list"
msgstr "编辑元数据对话框：在格式列表的右键菜单中，新增了“打开书籍文件夹”的操作选项。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Read aloud: Fix only first 32000 characters per chapter being read"
msgstr "朗读功能：修复了每章节仅能朗读前 32,000 个字符的限制问题。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: Read aloud: Fix clicking on a word to skip reading aloud to "
"that word causing word highlighting to stop working"
msgstr "内容服务器：修复了朗读功能的一个错误。此前，点击某个单词以跳转朗读进度，会导致单词高亮显示停止工作。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Linux: Handle speech dispatcher with dummy output module and no voices more "
