msgstr "内容服务器：修复了当界面语言非英语或书籍未设置语言时，无法修改书籍语言的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Linux: Read aloud with Piper: Fix audio not playing on some Linux systems"
msgstr "Linux：Piper 语音朗读：修复部分 Linux 系统无声音的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Notes browser: When searching books search over all currently selected "
