msgstr "备注浏览器：支持在所有选定分类中搜索书籍，而非仅限最后一个分类"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "18 Oct, 2024"
msgstr "18 Oct, 2024"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "PDF Input: Automatic header/footer detection and removal"
msgstr "PDF 输入：自动检测并移除页眉/页脚"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"A new, dedicated PDF Input engine for calibre that implements automatic "
"detection of headers and footers based on document analysis. The new engine "
"is the default to go back to using the old engine, select it in the PDF "
"Input section of the Conversion dialog."
msgstr ""
"Calibre 新增了专用的 PDF "
"输入引擎，能够基于文档分析自动检测并移除页眉和页脚。该新引擎为默认设置。若需切回使用旧引擎，请在转换对话框的“PDF 输入”部分进行选择。"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Read Aloud: Allow configuring an extra pause at the end of every sentence "
"when using the Piper TTS engine"
msgstr "语音朗读：支持配置 Piper 引擎在句尾的额外停顿"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"PDF Output: Add _WIDTH_PIXELS_ and _HEIGHT_PIXELS_ variables to know the "
"width and height of the header/footer area in templates"
msgstr "PDF 输出：为页眉/页脚模板新增 _WIDTH_PIXELS_ 与 _HEIGHT_PIXELS_ 变量，以识别该区域的像素宽度和高度"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Use calibre's bundled SSL certificates instead of the system "
"certificate store by default"
msgstr "Windows：网络连接默认采用 calibre 内置的 SSL 证书，不再依赖系统证书库"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Can be turned off via CALIBRE_USE_SYSTEM_CERTIFICATES=1 env var"
msgstr "可通过环境变量 CALIBRE_USE_SYSTEM_CERTIFICATES=1 禁用此功能"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Trim image tool: Add a control to adjust aspect ratio"
msgstr "图片裁剪工具：新增宽高比调节功能"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Kobo driver: Add support for the new firmware used by the Tolino Shine 5"
msgstr "Kobo 驱动：支持 Tolino Shine 5 的新固件"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression in previous release that broke copying of book to another "
