#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Content server: Fix embedding the server HTML inside a third party iframe "
"causing an error"
msgstr "内容服务器：解决在第三方网页 iframe 中嵌套内容服务器页面报错的故障"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "27 Sep, 2024"
msgstr "27 Sep, 2024"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Halve the time taken to open large EPUB format books for the "
"first time"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：将打开大型 EPUB 格式书籍的首次用时减半"

