msgstr "现在，一本四十万字的 EPUB 书籍在典型硬件上不到一秒即可打开"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "PDF new engine: Improve header/footer detection"
msgstr "PDF 新引擎：优化了对页眉和页脚的识别"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"For column icons and grid view emblems, support icons for both light and "
"dark themes"
msgstr "列图标与网格视图图标：支持深色/浅色主题双套图标"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"News downloads: Mark links to locally available articles with a middle-dot"
msgstr "新闻下载：在已下载至本地的文章链接旁添加间隔号 (·)标记"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
