"feel->Cover browser"
msgstr "窄屏布局：当窗口宽高比较小时，将封面浏览器置于书籍列表上方。可通过“首选项->外观->封面浏览器”控制"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Category notes browser: Add a button to search for books in the currently "
