msgstr "类别笔记浏览器：新增一个在当前选定类别中搜索书籍的按钮"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "Keyboard shortcut to toggle main window layout (Alt+Shift+L)"
msgstr "切换主窗口布局的快捷键 (Alt+Shift+L)"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Add the possibility to assign keyboard shortcuts to the tag browser sort "
"functions"
msgstr "支持为标签浏览器的排序功能分配快捷键"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression in the previous release that caused the cover browser to "
"not close when it is used as a separate window"
msgstr "修复上一版本中的一个回归错误，该错误曾导致封面浏览器作为独立窗口使用时无法关闭"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Fix a regression in the previous release that caused comments in the Book "
