msgstr "编辑书籍：修复特殊字符的高亮在编辑后不会立即更新，而是在后续操作后才更新的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Move Preferences to the left in the default toolbar, making it less likely "
"to be hidden behind an expander button on small screens"
msgstr "在默认工具栏中将“首选项”左移，降低其在小屏幕上被收纳按钮隐藏的可能性"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "05 Jan, 2024"
msgstr "05 Jan, 2024"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Tag browser: Allow displaying buttons next to items that have notes or links"
" for easy access. To enable these use Preferences->Look & feel->Tag browser"
msgstr "标签浏览器：允许在含有笔记或链接的项目旁显示按钮以便快速访问。可通过“首选项->外观->标签浏览器”开启"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Font subsetting: Preserve all OpenType layout features. This makes the "
