"using the subsetted font files in different contexts."
msgstr "字体子集化：保留所有 OpenType 布局特性。这虽会增大子集化后的字体文件体积，但能确保在不同语境下使用这些字体时不会出现视觉效果降级"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "macOS: Fix main calibre window not remembering its size on restart"
msgstr "macOS：修复 calibre 主窗口在重启后无法记住窗口大小的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Edit book: Fix the \"Show changes\" window moving down by a few pixels every"
