msgstr "编辑书籍：修复“显示更改”窗口每次打开时都会向下偏移几个像素的问题"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Amazon metadata download: Fixes for various changes to amazon website markup"
msgstr "Amazon 元数据下载：针对亚马逊网站标记语言的多处变动进行修复"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: When looking up words via Google in Europe pre-approve the "
