msgstr "Windows：内容服务器：修复上一版本中导致本地连接测试失效的回归错误"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Windows: Fix a regression that caused selections in the Book details panel "
"to be invisible"
msgstr "Windows：修复一个导致书籍详情面板中选中项不可见的回归错误"

